Package: HeartMetrics
Type: Package
Title: Functions for Biostatistics Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Kirthi Sri Lalitha Aki
Maintainer: Kirthi Sri Lalitha Aki <akikirthi@gmail.com>
Description: The BioMetrics package provides a set of functions for analyzing biostatistics data. The package includes functions for conducting t-tests, plotting Kaplan-Meier survival curves, and computing hazard ratios. The functions are designed to work with the heart dataset from the survival package, but can be easily adapted for use with other datasets.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
